metadata.name: Osiris
metadata.description: The red-haired Seth cut his brother Osiris into 14 pieces.  Osiris's wife, Isis, wanted to bring him back to life. Thanks to the wizard Amon, she was able to find all 13 pieces. Her genitalia was missing. Osiris painted the time he disappeared. How would Osiris, the god of good, explain what Seth, the god of evil, had done?
